Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:37.86,Te wo Tsunagou,,0,0,0,,your back is covered in mud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:45.41,Te wo Tsunagou,,0,0,0,,The pain of those scars will cheer you on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:49.21,Te wo Tsunagou,,0,0,0,,I want to join hands with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.99,Te wo Tsunagou,,0,0,0,,Even moreso during tough times,
